es5.alert.html.body:
ES5 Window方法

參考網址: 
http://www.w3schools.com/jsref/obj_window.asp

alert
通知視窗
alert('hello world');
confirm
確認視窗
var ask = confirm('choose one');

if (ask == true)
  alert('you choose OK');
else
  alert('you choose Cancel');
prompt
提示字元視窗
